# -*- coding: utf-8 -*-
"""9 new SEO FAQ entries with real search-query phrasing.
Each answer 500-900 chars, concrete, no filler. Used to inject into both the
visible accordion (index.html) and the FAQPage JSON-LD."""

# Each answer is a list of paragraphs (для <richtext> у видимому блоці).
